* Iron Raptor growled as she slowly opened her optics, this wasn't the 
clearing that she remembered. She sighed and squinted as the CR chamber 
opened and was swamped with light. The computer spoke...*

COMP: "Repair cycle...completed."

* Iron Raptor walked out slowly from the chamber and looked around, she was 
back in the Ark! She smiled a little in relieve, at least she was no longer 
tasting her own mech-fluid in her mouth.
She glanced up at a digital timer above the door to the room, she had been 
in repairs for nearly 2 mega-cycles.
Iron Raptor looked at her chest and snarled as she saw that it was fully 
repaired, she would have to thank the bot that brought her back to the Ark.*

" Computer, who brought me back?"

COMP: "Subject...Prowl."

* Iron Raptor smiled, she remembered when Rampage had thrown her into him 
and his cheeky comment afterwards. So, they were even now.*
